\c 7
\s Ukuphela sekufika
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kimi lisithi:
\v 2 Wena-ke, ndodana yomuntu, itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova kulo ilizwe lakoIsrayeli\x + Mal. 1.1. 2.11.\x*: Isiphetho, isiphetho sesifikile\x + 7.3,6. Lilo 4.18.\x* phezu kwamagumbi womane elizwe\x + Jobe 37.3.\x*.
\v 3 Khathesi isiphetho siphezu kwakho\x + 7.3,6. Lilo 4.18.\x*, njalo ngizathumela ukuthukuthela kwami phakathi kwakho, ngikwahlulele njengokwezenzo zakho\x + 7.8. 18.30.\x*, ngehlisele phezu kwakho wonke amanyala akho\x + 7.8. 18.30.\x*.
\v 4 Lelihlo lami\x + 7.9.\x* kaliyikukuhawukela\x + 5.11.\x*, kangiyikuyekela\x + 5.11.\x*, kodwa ngizakwehlisela izindlela zakho phezu kwakho\x + 7.9.\x*\x + 9.10. 11.21. 16.43. 22.31.\x*, lamanyala akho azakuba phakathi kwakho\x + 7.9.\x*. Khona lizakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 7.9,27. 6.7.\x*.
\v 5 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Ububi, ububi obubodwa, khangela, sebufikile.
\v 6 Isiphetho sesifikile, isiphetho sesifikile, siyakuvukela; khangela, sesifikile\x + 7.3,6. Lilo 4.18.\x*.
\v 7 Ukusa sekufikile kuwe, wena mhlali welizwe\x + 7.12. 12.22. 30.3. 7.10. Isa. 28.5.\x*; isikhathi sesifikile\x + 7.12. Zef. 1.14,15.\x*, usuku lwenkathazo luseduze\x + 7.10. 7.12. 12.22. 30.3. Isa. 28.5.\x*\x + Isa. 22.5.\x*, njalo kungeyisikho ukumemeza ngenjabulo kwezintaba\x + Jer. 25.30. Isa. 16.9. Isa. 22.5.\x*.
\v 8 Khathesi, kuseduze\x + Jobe 20.5.\x* ukuthi ngithululele ulaka lwami phezu kwakho\x + 9.8. 14.19. 20.8,13,21,33,34. 22.22. 21.31. 22.31.\x*, ngiphelelise intukuthelo yami phakathi kwakho\x + 5.13.\x*, ngikwahlulele njengokwezindlela zakho\x + 7.8. 18.30.\x*, ngehlisele phezu kwakho wonke amanyala akho\x + 7.8. 18.30.\x*.
\v 9 Lelihlo lami kaliyikuhawukela, njalo kangiyikuyekela\x + 7.9.\x*\x + 5.11.\x*; ngizanika njengokwezindlela zakho phezu kwakho\x + 7.8. 18.30.\x*, lamanyala akho azakuba phakathi kwakho\x + 7.9.\x*. Khona lizakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 7.9.\x*\x + 7.9,27. 6.7.\x* etshayayo\x + Isa. 9.13.\x*.
\v 10 Khangela usuku, khangela, selufikile; ukusa sekuphumile\x + 7.10,12. 12.22. 30.3. Isa. 28.5.\x*; intonga ihlumile, ukuziqhenya kukhahlele\x + 7.11. Isa. 10.5.\x*.
\v 11 Udlakela lusukume\x + 7.23. Jer. 6.7.\x* lwaba yintonga yobubi\x + 7.11. Isa. 10.5.\x*\x + Isa. 14.5.\x*; kakuyiku\add sala\add* kubo, hatshi-ke exukwini labo\x + 7.12,13,14.\x*, hatshi-ke okwabo, njalo kakuyikuba khona ukuqhinqa isililo phakathi kwabo\x + 24.16,23. Jer. 16.4,5,6.\x*.
\v 12 Isikhathi sesifikile, usuku selusondele\x + 7.12. Zef. 1.14,15.\x*; umthengi kangathokozi\x + Isa. 24.2.\x*, lomthengisi angalili\x + Isa. 24.2.\x*, ngoba ulaka\x + 7.14.\x* luphezu kwexuku lonke lalo\x + 7.12,13,14.\x*.
\v 13 Ngoba umthengisi kayikubuyela\x + Levi 25.13.\x* kokuthengisiweyo, lanxa impilo yabo isesephakathi kwabaphilayo\x + Levi 25.14,25,27-29,33,50.\x*; ngoba umbono mayelana lexuku lonke lalo kawuyikuphenduka\x + 7.12,13,14.\x*; futhi kakulamuntu ongaqinisa impilo yakhe ngesiphambeko sakhe.
\v 14 Baluvuthele uphondo ukuthi balungise konke, kodwa kakho oya empini\x + Jer. 4.5.\x*, ngoba ulaka lwami\x + 7.14.\x* luphezu kwexuku lalo lonke\x + 7.12,13,14.\x*.
\v 15 Inkemba ingaphandle\x + 6.11. Dute. 32.25. Lilo 1.20.\x*, lomatshayabhuqe wesifo\x + 6.11. Dute. 32.25. Lilo 1.20.\x* lendlala kungaphakathi\x + 6.11. Dute. 32.25. Lilo 1.20.\x*; osegangeni uzakufa ngenkemba\x + Jer. 14.18.\x*, losemzini indlala lomatshayabhuqe wesifo kuzamqeda\x + Jer. 14.18.\x*.
