\v 20 Lobuhle besiceciso sakhe\x + Isa. 4.2.\x* wabumisa ebukhosini\x + Isa. 4.2.\x*\x + 24.21. Isa. 2.10,19,21.\x*, kodwa benza kubo imifanekiso\x + 8.5-16. 16.17. Jer. 7.30. 2 Kho. 21.4.\x* yokunengekayo kwabo\x + 5.11.\x* \add le\add*zinengiso zabo\x + 5.11.\x*; ngenxa yalokho ngibumise bube yinto engcolileyo kubo.
\v 21 Njalo ngizakunikela\x + 11.9.\x* esandleni sabezizwe\x + 28.7. 7.22. 9.7. 24.21.\x* kube yimpango\x + 23.46. 25.7. 26.5. 34.8,22,28. 36.4,5. Jer. 30.16.\x*, lakwabakhohlakeleyo bomhlaba kube yimpango\x + 7.24.\x*, njalo bazakungcolisa\x + 28.7. 7.22. 9.7. 24.21.\x*.
